#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "Working with the &kappname; editor"
msgstr "&kappname; redaktori kasutamine"

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "Ülevaade"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kappname; editor is the editing area of the &kappname; window. This "
"editor is shared between &kate; and &kwrite;, and it can also be used in "
"&konqueror; for displaying text files from your local computer, or from the "
"network."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; redaktor kujutab endast &kappname; akna redigeerimisala. Sama "
"redaktorit kasutab ka &kwrite; ning seda võib kasutada ka &konqueror;is "
"tekstifailide näitamiseks, asugu need sinu arvutis või kuskil võrgus."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid "The editor is composed of the following components:"
msgstr "Redaktor koosneb järgmistest komponentidest:"

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid "The editing area"
msgstr "Redigeerimisala"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is where the text of your document is located."
msgstr "See on koht, kus asub dokumendi tekst."

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Scrollbars"
msgstr "Kerimisribad"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The scrollbars indicate the position of the visible part of the document "
"text, and can be used to move around the document. Dragging the scrollbars "
"will not cause the insertion cursor to be moved."
msgstr ""
"Kerimisribad osutavad dokumendi teksti nähtava osa asukohale ning neid saab "
"kasutada dokumendis liikumiseks. Kerimisriba kasutamine ei põhjusta siiski "
"automaatselt kursori asukoha muutust."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid "The scrollbars are displayed and hidden as required."
msgstr "Kerimisribasid võib soovikohaselt näidata või varjata."

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Icon Border"
msgstr "Ikoonipiire"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The icon border is a small pane on the left side of the editor, displaying a "
"small icon next to marked lines."
msgstr ""
"Ikoonipiire on väike riba redaktorist vasakul, mis näitab märgitud ridade "
"kõrval väikest ikooni."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can set or remove a <link linkend=\"kate-part-bookmarks\">bookmark</"
"link> in a visible line by clicking the &LMB; in the icon border next to "
"that line."
msgstr ""
"Nähtava rea <link linkend=\"kate-part-bookmarks\">järjehoidja</link> saab "
"paigaldada või eemaldada hiire vasaku nupu klõpsuga rea kõrval asuval "
"ikoonipiirdel."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The display of the icon border can be toggled using the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Icon Border</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Ikooniriba saab näidata või varjata menüükäsuga <menuchoice><guimenu>Vaade</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ikoonipiirde näitamine</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Line Numbers Pane"
msgstr "Reanumbrite paneel"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Line numbers pane shows the line numbers of all visible lines in the "
"document."
msgstr "Reanumbrite paneel osutab dokumendi kõigi nähtavate ridade numbreid."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The display of the Line Numbers Pane can be toggled using the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Line Numbers</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Reanumbrite paneeli saab näidata või varjata menüükäsuga "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Reanumbrite näitamine</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Folding Pane"
msgstr "Voltimispaneel"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The folding pane allows you to collapse or expand foldable blocks of lines. "
"The calculation of the foldable regions is done according to rules in the "
"syntax highlight definition for the document."
msgstr ""
"Voltimispaneel võimaldab avada või sulgeda volditavaid tekstiridu. "
"Volditavate piirkondade tuvastamine käib vastavalt dokumendi süntaksi "
"esiletõstmise definitsioonis leiduvatele reeglitele."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid "Also in this Chapter:"
msgstr "Selles peatükis on jutuks veel:"

#. Tag: link
#: part.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"kate-part-navigation\">Navigating in the Text</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"kate-part-navigation\">Tekstis liikumine</link>."

#. Tag: link
#: part.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"kate-part-selection\">Working with the Selection</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"kate-part-selection\">Valikute kasutamine</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: part.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-part-copy-and-paste\">Copying and Pasting Text</link>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-part-copy-and-paste\">Teksti kopeerimine ja asetamine</"
"link>"

#. Tag: link
#: part.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-part-find-replace\">Finding and Replacing Text</link>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-part-find-replace\">Teksti otsimine ja asendamine</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: part.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"kate-part-bookmarks\">Using Bookmarks</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"kate-part-bookmarks\">Järjehoidjate kasutamine</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: part.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatically Wrapping Text"
msgstr "Teksti automaatne reamurdmine"

#. Tag: link
#: part.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"kate-part-autoindent\">Using automatic indenting</link>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-part-autoindent\">Automaatse treppimise kasutamine</"
"link>"

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Navigating in the Text</title>"
msgstr "<title>Tekstis liikumine</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:99
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Moving around in the text in &kappname; is similar to most graphical text "
#| "editors. You move the cursor using the arrow keys and the <keycap>Page "
#| "Up</keycap>, <keycap>Page Down</keycap>, <keycap>Home</keycap> and "
#| "<keycap>End</keycap> keys in combination with the &Ctrl; and &Shift; "
#| "modifiers. The &Shift; key is always used to generate a selection, while "
#| "the &Ctrl; key has different effects on different keys:"
msgid ""
"Moving around in the text in &kappname; is similar to most graphical text "
"editors. You move the cursor using the arrow keys and the &PgUp;, &PgDn;, "
"&Home; and &End; keys in combination with the &Ctrl; and &Shift; modifiers. "
"The &Shift; key is always used to generate a selection, while the &Ctrl; key "
"has different effects on different keys:"
msgstr ""
"Tekstis liikumisel käitub &kappname; nagu iga teine graafiline "
"tekstiredaktor. Kursorit saab liigutada nooleklahvidega ning klahvidega "
"<keycap>Page Up</keycap>, <keycap>Page Down</keycap>, <keycap>Home</keycap> "
"ja <keycap>End</keycap>, millele võivad lisanduda muuteklahvid &Ctrl; ja "
"&Shift;. Klahviga &Shift; saab alati teksti valida, klahvil &Ctrl; on aga "
"erinevatele klahvidele mõnevõrra erinev tähendus:"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:106
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "For the <keycap>Up</keycap> and <keycap>Down</keycap> keys it means "
#| "scroll rather than move the cursor."
msgid ""
"For the &Up; and &Down; keys it means scroll rather than move the cursor."
msgstr ""
"Klahvide <keycap>Nool üles</keycap> ja <keycap>Nool alla</keycap> puhul "
"tähendab see kursori liigutamise asemel kerimist."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:108
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "For the <keycap>Left</keycap> and <keycap>Right</keycap> keys it means "
#| "skip words rather than characters."
msgid ""
"For the &Left; and &Right; keys it means skip words rather than characters."
msgstr ""
"Klahvide <keycap>Nool vasakule</keycap> ja <keycap>Nool paremale</keycap> "
"puhul tähendab see märkide asemel sõnakaupa liikumist."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:110
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "For the <keycap>Page Up</keycap> and <keycap>Page Down</keycap> keys it "
#| "means move to the visible edge of the view rather than browse."
msgid ""
"For the &PgUp; and &PgDn; keys it means move to the visible edge of the view "
"rather than browse."
msgstr ""
"Klahvide <keycap>Page Up</keycap> ja <keycap>Page Down</keycap> puhul "
"tähendab see leheküljekaupa liikumise asemel liikumist nähtava ala "
"vastavasse serva."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:113
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "For the <keycap>Home</keycap> and <keycap>End</keycap> keys it means move "
#| "to the beginning or end of the document rather than the beginning or end "
#| "of the line."
msgid ""
"For the &Home; and &End; keys it means move to the beginning or end of the "
"document rather than the beginning or end of the line."
msgstr ""
"Klahvide <keycap>Home</keycap> ja <keycap>End</keycap> puhul tähendab see "
"liikumise asemel rea algusse või lõppu liikumist dokumendi algusse või lõppu."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kappname; also provides you with a way to quickly jump to a matching brace "
"or parenthesis: place the cursor on the inside of a parenthesis or brace "
"character, and press <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>6</keycap></"
"keycombo> to jump to the matching parenthesis or brace."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; võimaldab ka kiiresti hüpata sulu paarilise juurde: vii kursor "
"sulumärgi juurde ja vajuta <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>6</"
"keycap></keycombo> ning liigudki antud sulu paarilise juurde."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In addition you can use <link linkend=\"kate-part-bookmarks\">bookmarks</"
"link> to quickly jump to positions that you define on your own."
msgstr ""
"Lisaks saab <link linkend=\"kate-part-bookmarks\">järjehoidjatega</link> "
"liikuda kiiresti enda määratud asukohta."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Working with the Selection</title>"
msgstr "<title>Valikute kasutamine</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are two basic ways of selecting text in &kappname;: using the mouse, "
"and using the keyboard."
msgstr ""
"&kappname;s saab teksti valida kahel viisil: hiire ja klaviatuuri abil."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To select using the mouse, hold down the &LMB; while dragging the mouse "
"cursor from where the selection should start, to the desired end point. The "
"text gets selected as you drag."
msgstr ""
"Hiirt eelistades hoia all hiire vasak nupp ja libista hiirekursor kohast, "
"kust soovid valikut alustada, kohani, kus soovid selle lõpetada. Selle "
"operatsiooniga ongi tekst valitud."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "Double-clicking a word will select that word."
msgstr "Topeltklõps sõnal valib selle sõna."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "Triple-clicking in a line will select the entire line."
msgstr "Kolmikklõps real valib terve rea."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid "If &Shift; is held down while clicking, text will be selected:"
msgstr ""
"Kui klõpsamise ajal hoida all klahvi &Shift;, valib see teksti järgmiselt:"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If nothing is already selected, from the text cursor position to the mouse "
"cursor position."
msgstr ""
"kui midagi ei olnud valitud, siis teksti sisestuskursori asukohast "
"hiirekursori asukohani."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If there is a selection, from and including that selection to the mouse "
"cursor position."
msgstr ""
"kui midagi oli juba valitud, siis sealt alates (kaasa arvatud valitu) "
"hiirekursori asukohani."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When selecting text by dragging the mouse, the selected text is copied to "
"the clipboard, and can be pasted by clicking the middle mouse button in the "
"editor, or in any other application to which you want to paste the text."
msgstr ""
"Kui teksti valitakse hiirt lohistades, kopeeritakse valitud tekst "
"lõikepuhvrisse ja seda saab asetada, klõpsates hiire keskmise klahviga "
"redaktoris või mõnes muus rakenduses, kuhu soovid teksti asetada."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:161
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To select using the keyboard, hold down the &Shift; key while using the "
#| "navigation keys (Arrow keys, <keycap>Page Up</keycap>, <keycap>Page Down</"
#| "keycap>, <keycap>Home</keycap> and <keycap>End</keycap>, possibly in "
#| "combination with &Ctrl; to extend the move of the text cursor)."
msgid ""
"To select using the keyboard, hold down the &Shift; key while using the "
"navigation keys (Arrow keys, &PgUp;, &PgDn;, &Home; and &End;, possibly in "
"combination with &Ctrl; to extend the move of the text cursor)."
msgstr ""
"Klaviatuuri eelistades hoia alla klahvi &Shift; ning rakenda liikumisklahve "
"(nooleklahvid ning klahvid <keycap>Page Up</keycap>, <keycap>Page Down</"
"keycap>, <keycap>Home</keycap> ja <keycap>End</keycap>). Võimalik on ka "
"kombinatsioon klahviga &Ctrl;, mis laiendab tekstikursori liikumist."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See also the section <link linkend=\"kate-part-navigation\">Navigating in "
"the Text</link> in this chapter."
msgstr ""
"Vaata ka samas peatükis sektsiooni <link linkend=\"kate-part-navigation"
"\">Tekstis liikumine</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To <action>Copy</action> the current selection, use the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu item or the keyboard shortcut (defaults to <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>)."
msgstr ""
"Sooritamaks aktiivse valiku <action>kopeerimine</action>, kasuta menüükäsku "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Redigeerimine</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kopeeri</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> või kiirklahvi (vaikimisi <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>)."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To <action>Deselect</action> the current selection, use the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Deselect</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu item, or the keyboard shortcut (default is <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo>), or click with the "
"&LMB; in the editor."
msgstr ""
"Andmaks käsku <action>Tühista valik</action>, kasuta menüükäsku "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Redigeerimine</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Tühista valik</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, kiirklahvi (vaikimisi <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo>) või klõpsa redaktoris hiire "
"vasaku nupuga."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Block Selection"
msgstr "Plokivaliku kasutamine"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When Block Selection is enabled, you can make <quote>vertical selections</"
"quote> in the text, meaning selecting limited columns from multiple lines. "
"This is handy for working with tab separated lines for example."
msgstr ""
"Kui blokivalik on sisse lülitatud, saad sooritada tekstis "
"<quote>vertikaalseid valikuid</quote>, mis tähendab teatud arvu veergude "
"valimist mitmes reas. See võib olla kasulik näiteks tabulaatori abil "
"eraldatud ridade puhul."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Block Selection can be toggled using the <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Block Selection Mode</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. The "
"default keyboard shortcut is <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;"
"<keycap>B</keycap> </keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Blokivaliku saab sisse/välja lülitada menüükäsuga "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Redigeerimine</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Blokivaliku "
"režiim</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Vaikimisi kiirklahv on <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>B</keycap> </keycombo>."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Overwrite Selection"
msgstr "Valiku ülekirjutamine"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If Overwrite Selection is enabled, typing or pasting text into the selection "
"will cause the selected text to be replaced. If not enabled, new text will "
"be added at the position of the text cursor."
msgstr ""
"Kui valiku ülekirjutamine on sisse lülitatud, põhjustab kirjutamine või "
"teksti asetamine valitud teksti alal selle asendamise. Kui see ei ole sisse "
"lülitatud, lisatakse uus tekst tekstikursori asukohta."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid "Overwrite Selection is enabled by default."
msgstr "Vaikimisi on valiku ülekirjutamine sisse lülitatud."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the setting for this option, use the <link linkend=\"pref-edit-"
"cursor-selection\">Cursor &amp; Selection</link> page of the <link linkend="
"\"config-dialog\">Configuration Dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Selle võimaluse muutmiseks kasuta <link linkend=\"config-dialog"
"\">seadistustedialoogi</link> lehekülge <link linkend=\"pref-edit-cursor-"
"selection\">Kursor ja valimine</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Persistent Selection"
msgstr "Püsiva valiku kasutamine"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When Persistent Selection is enabled, typing characters or moving the cursor "
"will not cause the Selection to become deselected. This means that you can "
"move the cursor away from the selection and type text."
msgstr ""
"Kui püsiv valik on sisse lülitatud, ei põhjusta märkide sisestamine või "
"kursori liigutamine valiku tühistamist. See tähendab, et kursori võib "
"liigutada valitud alalt mujale ja asuda teksti sisestama."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid "Persistent Selection is disabled by default."
msgstr "Vaikimisi on püsiv valik välja lülitatud."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Persistent Selection can be enabled in the <link linkend=\"pref-edit-cursor-"
"selection\">Cursor &amp; Selection</link> page of the <link linkend=\"config-"
"dialog\">Configuration Dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Püsiva valiku saab sisse lülitada <link linkend=\"config-dialog"
"\">seadistustedialoogi</link> leheküljel <link linkend=\"pref-edit-cursor-"
"selection\">Kursor ja valimine</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If Persistent Selection and Overwrite Selection are both enabled, typing or "
"pasting text when the text cursor is inside the selection will cause it to "
"be replaced and deselected."
msgstr ""
"Kui sisse on lülitatud nii püsiv valik kui valiku ülekirjutamine, põhjustab "
"kirjutamine või teksti asetamine juhul, kui kursor asetseb valitud alal, nii "
"teksti asendamist kui valiku tühistamist."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Copying and Pasting Text</title>"
msgstr "<title>Teksti kopeerimine ja asetamine</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To copy text, select it and use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. Additionally, "
"selecting text with the mouse will cause selected text to be copied to the X "
"selection."
msgstr ""
"Teksti kopeerimiseks vali see ja kasuta menüükäsku "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Redigeerimine</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kopeeri</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Teksti valimine hiirega põhjustab samuti selle "
"kopeerimise lõikepuhvrisse."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To paste the text currently in the clipboard, use the <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu "
"item."
msgstr ""
"Lõikepuhvris asetseva teksti asetamiseks kasuta menüükäsku "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Redigeerimine</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Aseta</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:256
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Additionally, text selected with the mouse may be pasted by clicking the "
#| "<mousebutton>middle</mousebutton> mouse button at the desired position."
msgid ""
"Additionally, text selected with the mouse may be pasted by clicking the "
"&MMB; at the desired position."
msgstr ""
"Lisaks võib hiirega valitud teksti asetada, kui sooritada soovitud kohas "
"klõps hiire <mousebutton>keskmise</mousebutton> nupuga."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are using the &kde; desktop, you can retrieve earlier copied text "
"from any application using the &klipper; icon in the system tray."
msgstr ""
"Kui kasutad &kde; töölauda, võid asetada suvalises rakenduses varem "
"kopeeritud teksti, kasutades süsteemse salve ikooni &klipper;."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Finding and Replacing Text</title>"
msgstr "<title>Teksti otsimine ja asendamine</title>"

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Search and Replace Bars"
msgstr "Otsimis- ja asendamisribad"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kappname; has an incremental search bar and a power search and replace bar, "
"which offers the means of entering a replacement string along with a few "
"extra options."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; võimaldab kasutada nii täpsustava otsingu kui ka võimsa otsimis- "
"ja asendamisriba võimalusi, mis pakuvad võimalust sisestada asendatav tekst "
"koos mõne lisavalikuga."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid "The bars offer the following common options:"
msgstr "Ribad pakuvad järgmisi tavapäraseid võimalusi:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: part.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find"
msgstr "Otsing"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:285
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is where to enter the search string. The interpretation of the string "
"depends on some of the options described below."
msgstr ""
"Siia saab sisestada otsimisstringi. Selle tõlgendamine sõltub mõningatest "
"edaspidi kirjeldatavatest võimalustest."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: part.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid "Match case"
msgstr "Tõstutundlik"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, the search will be limited to entries that match the case (upper "
"or lower) of each of the characters in the search pattern."
msgstr ""
"Sisselülitamisel piirdub otsing vastetega, mille kõigi tähtede tähesuurus "
"(väikesed või suured tähed) on täpselt samasugused nagu otsingusõnal."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid "The power search and replace bar offers some additional options:"
msgstr "Võimas otsimis- ja asendamisriba pakub mõningaid lisavõimalusi:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: part.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plain Text"
msgstr "Lihttekst"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:307
#, no-c-format
msgid "Literally match any occurrence of the search string."
msgstr "Leitakse täpselt kõik otsingustringi vasted."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: part.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid "Whole Words"
msgstr "Terved sõnad"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If selected, the search will only match if there is a word boundary at both "
"ends of the string matching, meaning not an alphanumeric character - either "
"some other visible character or a line end."
msgstr ""
"Selle valimisel otsitakse ainult selliseid vasteid, mille puhul "
"otsimisstringile vastab mõlemalt poolt eristatav sõna, mis ei tähenda tärki "
"- ei mingit nähtavat märki ega realõppu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: part.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid "Escape Sequences"
msgstr "Paojadad"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If selected, the <guibutton>Add</guibutton> menuitem at the bottom of the "
"context menu of the text boxes will be enabled and allows you to add escape "
"sequences to the search pattern from a predefined list."
msgstr ""
"Selle valimisel saab kasutada tekstikastide kontekstimenüü kirjet "
"<guibutton>Lisa</guibutton>, mis lubab lisada eelnevalt määratud nimekirjast "
"otsingufraasi paojadasid."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: part.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid "Regular Expression"
msgstr "Regulaaravaldis"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If selected, the search string is interpreted as a regular expression. The "
"<guibutton>Add</guibutton> menuitem at the bottom of the context menu of the "
"text boxes will be enabled and allows you to add regular expression items to "
"the search pattern from a predefined list."
msgstr ""
"Selle valimisel tõlgendatakse otsimisstringi regulaaravaldisena. Samuti saab "
"kasutada tekstikastide kontekstimenüü kirjet <guibutton>Lisa</guibutton>, "
"mis lubab lisada eelnevalt määratud nimekirjast otsingufraasi "
"regulaaravaldise elemente."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:339
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See <link linkend=\"regular-expressions\">Regular Expressions</link> for "
"more on these."
msgstr ""
"Vaata lähemalt peatükki <link linkend=\"regular-expressions"
"\">Regulaaravaldised</link>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: part.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search in the selection only"
msgstr "Otsing ainult valikus"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:347
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, the search and replace will be performed within the selected "
"text only."
msgstr "Sisselülitamisel toimub otsimine ja asendamine ainult valitud tekstis."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: part.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find all"
msgstr "Otsi kõik"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking this button highlights all matches in the document and shows the "
"number of found matches in a small popup."
msgstr ""
"Sellele nupule klõpsates tõstetakse dokumendis esile kõik sobivad vasted ja "
"näidatakse leitud vastete arvu väikese hüpikteatega."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid "Finding Text"
msgstr "Teksti otsimine"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:367
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To find text, launch the incremental search bar with <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> or from the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Find...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Teksti otsimiseks käivita täpsustava otsingu riba kiirklahviga <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> või menüükäsuga "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Redigeerimine</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Otsi...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:371
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This opens the incremental search bar at the bottom of the editor window. On "
"the left side of the bar is a button with an icon to close the bar, followed "
"by a small text box for entering the search pattern."
msgstr ""
"See avab redaktoriakna allosas täpsustava otsingu riba. Riba vasakus servas "
"on ikooniga nupp selle sulgemiseks, mille kõrval asub tekstikast, kuhu saab "
"sisestada otsingusõna."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start entering the characters of your search pattern, the search "
"starts immediately. If there is a match in the text this is highlighted and "
"the background color of the entry field changes to light green. If the "
"search pattern does not match any string in the text, this is indicated by a "
"light red background color of the entry field."
msgstr ""
"Otsingusõna sisestades hakatakse seda kohe otsima. Kui leitakse vaste, "
"tõstetakse see esile ning kirje enda taust muutub heleroheliseks. Kui "
"otsingusõnale tekstis vastet ei leita, annab sellest märku tekstikasti "
"helepunane taust."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:378 part.docbook:422
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"arrow-up-"
"double-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> or "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"arrow-down-double-22.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> button to jump to the "
"next or previous match in the document."
msgstr ""
"Nupuga <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"arrow-up-"
"double-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> või "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"arrow-down-double-22.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> saab hüpata leitu "
"järgmisele või eelmisele esinemiskohale dokumendis."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Matches in the document are highlighted even when you close the search bar. "
"To clear this highlighting, press the &Esc; key."
msgstr ""
"Vasted on dokumendis esile tõstetud isegi siis, kui sulged otsinguriba. "
"Esiletõstmise kõrvaldamiseks tuleb vajutada klahvi &Esc;."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:384
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can choose whether the search should be case sensitive. Selecting "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"format-text-"
"superscript-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> will "
"limit finds to entries that match the case (upper or lower) of each of the "
"characters in the search pattern."
msgstr ""
"Saab valida, kas otsing on tõstutundlik. Kui valida "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"format-text-"
"superscript-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>, "
"piirdub otsing vastetega, mille kõigi tähtede tähesuurus (väikesed või "
"suured tähed) on täpselt samasugused nagu otsingusõnal."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:388
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"configure-"
"shortcuts-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> button "
"at the right side of the incremental search bar to switch to the power "
"search and replace bar."
msgstr ""
"Paremas servas asuvale nupule <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata "
"fileref=\"configure-shortcuts-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject> klõpsates saab avada võimsa otsimis- ja asendamisriba."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To repeat the last find operation, if any, without calling the incremental "
"search bar, use <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul"
"\"><keycap>F3</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Find Next</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or "
"<menuchoice><shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F3</"
"keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Find "
"Previous</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Viimase otsingu kordamiseks ilma võimsat otsinguriba avamata kasuta "
"<menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F3</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Redigeerimine</guimenu><guimenuitem>Otsi "
"järgmine</guimenuitem></menuchoice> või <menuchoice><shortcut> <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F3</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Redigeerimine</guimenu><guimenuitem>Otsi eelmine</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid "Replacing Text"
msgstr "Teksti asendamine"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To replace text, launch the power search and replace bar using the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Replace</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> command, or the <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</"
"keycap></keycombo> shortcut."
msgstr ""
"Teksti asendamiseks käivita võimas otsimis- ja asendamisriba menüükäsuga "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Redigeerimine</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Asenda</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> või kiirklahviga <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:412
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "On the upper left side of the bar is a button with an icon to close the "
#| "bar, followed by a small text box for entering the search pattern."
msgid ""
"On the upper left side of the bar is a button with an icon to close the bar, "
"followed by a small combo box for entering the search pattern. The box "
"remembers recently used patterns."
msgstr ""
"Riba vasakus servas ülal asub ikooniga nupp selle sulgemiseks, mille kõrval "
"paikneb väike tekstikast otsingusõna sisestamiseks."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can control the search mode by selecting the options <guilabel>Plain "
"Text</guilabel>, <guilabel>Whole Words</guilabel>, <guilabel>Escape "
"Sequences</guilabel> or <guilabel>Regular Expression</guilabel> from the "
"drop down box."
msgstr ""
"Otsingurežiimi saab juhtida valikutega <guilabel>Lihttekst</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Terved sõnad</guilabel>, <guilabel>Paojadad</guilabel> ja "
"<guilabel>Regulaaravaldis</guilabel>, mida on kirjeldatud eespool."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:418
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Escape sequences</guilabel> or <guilabel>Regular expression</"
"guilabel> are selected, the <guibutton>Add...</guibutton> menuitem at the "
"bottom of the context menu of the text boxes will be enabled and allows you "
"to add escape sequences or regular expression items to the search or replace "
"pattern from predefined lists."
msgstr ""
"Kui valitud on <guilabel>Paojadad</guilabel> või <guilabel>Regulaaravaldis</"
"guilabel>, aktiveerub tekstikastide kontekstimenüü allosas menüükirje "
"<guibutton>Lisa...</guibutton>, mis lubab lisada otsimis- või "
"asendamismustrisse paojadasid või regulaaravaldisi eelnevalt määratud "
"nimekirjast."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:426
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the text to replace with in the text box labeled <guilabel>Replace</"
"guilabel> and click the <guibutton>Replace</guibutton> button to replace "
"only the highlighted text or the <guibutton>Replace All</guibutton> button "
"to replace the search text in the whole document."
msgstr ""
"Sisesta asendustekst kasti <guilabel>Asendus</guilabel> ja klõpsa nupule "
"<guibutton>Asenda</guibutton> ainult esile tõstetud teksti asendamiseks või "
"<guibutton>Asenda kõik</guibutton> otsinguteksti asendamiseks kogu "
"dokumendis."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:430
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can modify the search and replace behavior by selecting different "
"options at the bottom of the bar. Selecting "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"format-text-"
"superscript-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> will "
"limit finds to entries that match the case (upper or lower) of each of the "
"characters in the search pattern. <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata "
"fileref=\"edit-select-all-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject> will search and replace within the current selection "
"only. The <guilabel>Find All</guilabel> button highlights all matches in the "
"document and shows the number of found matches in a small popup."
msgstr ""
"Otsimise ja asendamise käitumist saab muuta erinevate valikutega riba "
"allservas. Kui valida <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"format-text-superscript-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>, piiratakse otsing sõnadega, mille puhul valitseb täielik "
"vastavus otsingumõistele ka suur- ja väiketähtedes. "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-select-all-22.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> otsib ja asendab "
"ainult aktiivse valiku piires. Nupuga <guilabel>Otsi kõik</guilabel> saab "
"esile tõsta kõik dokumendis leiduvad vasted ning ühtlasi näeb väikeses "
"hüpikdialoogis leitud vastete arvu."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:440
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"configure-"
"shortcuts-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> button "
"at the right side of the power search and replace bar to switch to the "
"incremental search bar."
msgstr ""
"Riba paremas servas asuvale nupule "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"configure-shortcuts-22."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> klõpsates saab "
"avada võimsa otsimis- ja asendamisriba."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:445
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are using a regular expression to find the text to replace, you can "
"employ backreferences to reuse text captured in parenthesized subpatterns of "
"the expression."
msgstr ""
"Kui kasutad asendamisel teksti otsimiseks regulaaravaldisi, on sul võimalus "
"tarvitada ka tagasiviitu avaldise sulgudes oleva alammustriga haaratud "
"teksti taaskasutamiseks."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See <link linkend=\"regular-expressions\">Regular Expressions</link> for "
"more on those."
msgstr ""
"Vaata lähemalt peatükki <link linkend=\"regular-expressions"
"\">Regulaaravaldised</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:451
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can do <command>find</command>, <command>replace</command> and "
"<command>ifind</command> (incremental search) from the <link linkend="
"\"advanced-editing-tools-commandline\">command line</link>."
msgstr ""
"Kirjeldatuga toimetulevaid käske <command>find</command> (otsimine), "
"<command>replace</command> (asendamine) ja <command>ifind</command> "
"(täpsustav otsing) saab kasutada ka <link linkend=\"advanced-editing-tools-"
"commandline\">käsureal</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:461
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Using Bookmarks</title>"
msgstr "<title>Järjehoidjate kasutamine</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:463
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The bookmarks feature allows you to mark certain lines, to be able to easily "
"find them again."
msgstr ""
"Järjehoidjad võimaldavad märkida teatud ridu, et neid hiljem vajaduse korral "
"hõlpsasti leida."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:466
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can set or remove a bookmark in a line in two ways:"
msgstr "Järjehoidjaid võib reaga siduda või eemaldada kahel viisil:"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:470
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Move the insertion cursor to the line and activate the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu><guimenuitem>Set Bookmark</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>B</"
"keycap></keycombo>) command."
msgstr ""
"liigutades tekstikursori soovitud reale ja kasutades kas menüükäsku "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Järjehoidjad</guimenu><guimenuitem>Sea järjehoidja</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> või kiirklahviga <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>B</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:476
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click in the Icon Border next to the line."
msgstr "klõpsates rea kõrval asuval ikoonipiirdel."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:481
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Bookmarks are available in the <guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> menu. The "
"individual bookmarks are available as menu items, labeled with the line "
"number of the line with the bookmark, and the first few characters of the "
"text in the line. To move the insertion cursor to the beginning of a "
"bookmarked line, open the menu and select the bookmark."
msgstr ""
"Järjehoidjaid näeb menüüs <guimenu>Järjehoidjad</guimenu>. Iga järjehoidja "
"on seal kättesaadav menüüelemendina, teda märgib reanumber ja selle rea "
"mõned esimesed märgid. Tekstikursori liigutamiseks järjehoidjaga tähistatud "
"rea algusesse ava menüü ja vali vajalik järjehoidja."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:488
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To quickly move between bookmarks or to the next/previous bookmark, use "
#| "the <menuchoice><guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu><guimenuitem>Next</"
#| "guimenuitem> </menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; "
#| "<keycap>PgDown</keycap></keycombo>) or <menuchoice> <guimenu>Bookmarks</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Previous</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo "
#| "action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>PgUp</keycap> </keycombo>) commands."
msgid ""
"To quickly move between bookmarks or to the next/previous bookmark, use the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu><guimenuitem>Next</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&PgDn;</keycombo>) or "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu><guimenuitem>Previous</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&PgUp;</"
"keycombo>) commands."
msgstr ""
"Järjehoidjate vahel liikumiseks või suundumiseks järgmisele/eelmisele "
"järjehoidjale kasuta käske <menuchoice><guimenu>Järjehoidjad</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Järgmine</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> (<keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Alt; <keycap>PgDown</keycap></keycombo>) ja <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Järjehoidjad</guimenu><guimenuitem>Eelmine</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>PgUp</keycap> </"
"keycombo>)."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:498
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatically Wrapping text"
msgstr "Automaatne reamurdmine"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:500
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This feature allows you to have the text formatted in a very simple way: the "
"text will be wrapped, so that no lines exceed a maximum number of characters "
"per line, unless there is a longer string of non-whitespace characters."
msgstr ""
"See võimalus lubab teksti vormindada äärmiselt lihtsalt: read murtakse, nii "
"et ükski rida ei ületa määratud tähtede arvu, kui ei esine just pikem ilma "
"tühikuteta string."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:504
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To enable/disable it, check/uncheck the <guibutton>Static Word Wrap</"
"guibutton> checkbox in the <link linkend=\"pref-word-wrap\">edit page</link> "
"of the <link linkend=\"config-dialog\">configuration dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Selle lubamiseks või keelamiseks tee või eemalda märge <link linkend="
"\"config-dialog\">seadistustedialoogi</link> lehekülje <link linkend=\"pref-"
"word-wrap\">Redigeerimine</link> kastist <guibutton>Staatiline reamurdmine</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:507
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To set the maximum line width (maximum characters per line), use the <link "
"linkend=\"pref-wrap-words-at\"><guibutton>Wrap Words At</guibutton></link> "
"option in the <link linkend=\"pref-edit\">Editing</link> page of the <link "
"linkend=\"config-dialog\">configuration dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Rea maksimumpikkuse määramiseks (maksimaalne märkide arv rea kohta) kasuta "
"<link linkend=\"config-dialog\">seadistustedialoogi</link> lehekülje <link "
"linkend=\"pref-edit\">Redigeerimine</link> valikut <link linkend=\"pref-wrap-"
"words-at\"><guibutton>Reamurdmise veerg</guibutton></link>."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:512
#, no-c-format
msgid "If enabled, it has the following effects:"
msgstr "Kui see on sisse lülitatud, ilmnevad järgmised mõjud:"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:516
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"While typing, the editor will automatically insert a hard line break after "
"the last whitespace character at a position before the maximum line width is "
"reached."
msgstr ""
"kirjutamise ajal lisab redaktor automaatselt sunniviisilise reamurdmise "
"märgi viimase tühiku järele enne rea maksimaalse pikkuse saavutamist."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:518
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"While loading a document, the editor will wrap the text in a similar way, so "
"that no lines are longer than the maximum line width, if they contain any "
"whitespace allowing that."
msgstr ""
"dokumendi laadimisel murrab redaktor read samal põhimõttel, et ükski rida ei "
"oleks pikem lubatud maksimumist, kui neis muidugi esineb reamurdmist "
"võimaldav tühik."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:524
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "There is currently no way to set word wrap for document types, or even to "
#| "enable or disable the feature on a per document level. This will be fixed "
#| "in a future version of &kappname;"
msgid ""
"There is currently no way to set word wrap for document types, or even to "
"enable or disable the feature on a per document level. This will be fixed in "
"a future version of &kappname;."
msgstr ""
"Praegu puudub võimalus määrata reamurdmine erinevatele dokumenditüüpidele, "
"seda ei saa ka dokumendi tasandil lubada või keelata. Neid võimalusi "
"rakendab &kappname; tulevikus."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:530
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Using automatic indenting</title>"
msgstr "<title>Automaatse treppimise kasutamine</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:532
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kappname;s editor component supports a variety of autoindenting modes, "
#| "designed for different text formats. You can pick from the available "
#| "modes using the <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
#| "guimenu><guisubmenu>Indentation</guisubmenu></menuchoice> menu. The "
#| "autoindent modules also provide a function <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Align</guimenuitem></menuchoice> which will "
#| "recalculate the indentation of the selected or current line. Thus, you "
#| "may reindent your entire document by selecting all the text and "
#| "activating that action."
msgid ""
"&kappname;s editor component supports a variety of autoindenting modes, "
"designed for different text formats. You can pick from the available modes "
"using the <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guisubmenu>Indentation</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> menu. The autoindent modules also provide a "
"function <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Format "
"Indentation</guimenuitem></menuchoice> which will recalculate the "
"indentation of the selected or current line. Thus, you may reindent your "
"entire document by selecting all the text and activating that action."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; redaktor pakub mitmeid automaatse treppimise viise vastavalt "
"erinevatele tekstivormingutele. Sobiva režiimi saab valida menüüst "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Tööriistad</guimenu><guisubmenu>Treppimine</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice>. Automaatse treppimise moodul pakub ka võimaluse "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Tööriistad</guimenu><guimenuitem>Joonda</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>, mis arvutab välja valitud või aktiivse rea taande. Nii on "
"võimalik kogu dokumendi treppimine korraga teha, valides kogu teksti ja siis "
"selle toimingu."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:541
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All the indent modes use the indentation related settings in the active "
"document."
msgstr ""
"Kõik treppimisrežiimid kasutavad aktiivse dokumendi treppimisseadistusi."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:544
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can set all sorts of configuration variables, including those related to "
"indentation using <link linkend=\"config-variables\">Document Variables</"
"link> and <link linkend=\"pref-open-save-modes-filetypes\">File types</link>."
msgstr ""
"Treppimisele on võimalik määrata mitmesuguseid muutujaid, sealhulgas saab "
"seda teha seadistustedialoogi leheküljel <link linkend=\"pref-open-save-"
"modes-filetypes\">Failitüübid</link> kirjega <link linkend=\"config-variables"
"\">Dokumendi muutujad</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:551
#, no-c-format
msgid "Available Autoindent Modes"
msgstr "Võimalikud automaatse treppimise režiimid"

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:554
#, no-c-format
msgid "None"
msgstr "Puudub"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:555
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting this mode turns automatic indenting off entirely."
msgstr "Selle valimine lülitab automaatse treppimise täielikult välja."

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:560
#, no-c-format
msgid "Normal"
msgstr "Tavaline"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:561
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This indenter simply keeps the indentation similar to the previous line with "
"any content other than whitespace. You can combine this with using the "
"indent and unindent actions for indenting to your own taste."
msgstr ""
"See režiim säilitab lihtsalt treppimise sellisena, nagu see esines eelmisel "
"real, kui rida alustab midagi muud kui tühimärk. Seda saab kombineerida "
"treppimise ja treppimise eemaldamise toimingutega, et anda tekstile just "
"selline taane, nagu sulle meeldib või nagu sulle vaja."

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:567
#, no-c-format
msgid "C Style"
msgstr "C stiil"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:568
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "An indenter for C and similar languages, such as C++, C#, java, "
#| "javascript and so on. This indenter will not work with scripting "
#| "languages such as Perl or PHP."
msgid ""
"An indenter for C and similar languages, such as C++, C#, &Java;, "
"&javascript; and so on. This indenter will not work with scripting languages "
"such as Perl or PHP."
msgstr ""
"Režiim C ja teistele sarnastele keeltele, näiteks C++, C#, Java, JavaScript "
"ja nii edasi. See ei toimi skriptikeelte puhul (näiteks Perl või PHP)."

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:574
#, no-c-format
msgid "Haskell"
msgstr "Haskell"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:575
#, no-c-format
msgid "An indenter for the functional programming language Haskell."
msgstr "Funktsionaalne programmeerimiskeele Haskell treppimise korrastaja."

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:580
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lilypond"
msgstr "Lilypond"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:581
#, no-c-format
msgid "An indenter for the Lilypond notation language for music."
msgstr "Muusika märgistuskeele Lilypond treppimise korrastaja."

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:586
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lisp"
msgstr "Lisp"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:587
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An indenter specifically for the Lisp scripting language and Lisp dialects."
msgstr ""
"Spetsiaalselt skriptikeelele Lisp ja selle dialektidele mõeldud treppimise "
"korrastaja."

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:593
#, no-c-format
msgid "Python"
msgstr "Python"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:594
#, no-c-format
msgid "An indenter specifically for the python scripting language."
msgstr "Spetsiaalselt skriptikeelele Python mõeldud režiim."

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:599
#, no-c-format
msgid "XML Style"
msgstr "XML stiil"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:600
#, no-c-format
msgid "An indenter specifically for XML like languages."
msgstr "Spetsiaalselt XML-i sarnastele keeltele mõeldud treppija."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:609
#, no-c-format
msgid "Line Modification Indicators"
msgstr "Rea muutmise tähised"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:611
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kappname;'s line modification indicators let you easily see what you have "
"recently changed in a file. By default, saved changes are indicated by a "
"green bar to the left of a document, while unsaved changes are indicated by "
"an orange bar."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; rea muutmise tähised võimaldavad hõlpsalt näha, mida oled failis "
"viimati muutnud. Salvestatud muudatusi tähistab roheline riba dokumendist "
"vasakul, salvestamata muudatusi oranž riba."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:619
#, no-c-format
msgid "Line Modification Indicators in action."
msgstr "Rea muutmise tähised."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:623
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can change the colors used in the <link linkend=\"prefcolors"
"\"><guilabel>Fonts &amp; Colors</guilabel> configuration panel</link>, or "
"you can disable this feature completely in the <link linkend=\"appearance-"
"borders\"><guilabel>Borders</guilabel> tab of the <guilabel>Appearance</"
"guilabel> configuration panel</link>."
msgstr "Soovi korral võib selle omaduse käsurealt välja lülitada:"

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:632
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Scrollbar Minimap"
msgstr "Kerimisriba minikaart"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:634
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kappname;'s Scrollbar Minimap displays a preview of documents in place of "
"the scrollbar. The currently visible portion of the document is highlighted."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; kerimisriba minikaart näitab kerimisriba kohal dokumentide "
"eelvaatlust. Parajasti nähtav dokumendi osa on esile tõstetud."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:641
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Scrollbar Minimap shows a preview of the &kate; source code."
msgstr "Kerimisriba minikaart näitab &kate; lähtekoodi eelvaatlust."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:646
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can temporarily enable or disable the minimap by selecting "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>View Scrollbar Minimap</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> or permanently in <link linkend=\"appearance-"
"borders\">the Appearance section of &kappname;'s configuration</link>."
msgstr ""
"Minikaardi saab ajutiselt sisse või välja lülitada menüükäsuga "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Vaade</guimenu><guimenuitem>Kerimisriba minikaardi "
"näitamine</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, püsivalt aga <link linkend="
"\"appearance-borders\">&kappname; seadistusdialoogi välimuse sektsioonis</"
"link>."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:654
#, no-c-format
msgid "Multiple cursors"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:656
#, no-c-format
msgid "Multiple cursor support was introduced with version 5.93 of katepart."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:659
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating multiple cursors"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:662
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create them via mouse, use &Alt; + &LMB;. The modifier is configurable, "
"see <link linkend=\"multicursor-modifier-configure\">Configure multicursor "
"modifier</link>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:664
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create via keyboard, press <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Up;</"
"keycombo> to create cursor above primary cursor and <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Down;</keycombo> to create cursor below. These shortcuts are "
"also configurable"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:666
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create cursors out of a selection, first select some text and then press "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;&Alt;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo>. This "
"will create a cursor at the end of each line in selection."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:668
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> to find "
"the next occurrence of the word under cursor and select it + create a "
"cursor. If you want to skip the current word under cursor, press <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>K</keycap></keycombo> and it will mark the "
"currently selected word as skipped. When you press <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Alt;<keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> again it will unselect the current "
"word and move to the next word."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:671
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Shift;<keycap>J</keycap></"
"keycombo> to find all occurrences of the word under cursor and select them "
"with a cursor at the end of each selection. You can use <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> to cycle through the selected "
"words and use <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>K</keycap></keycombo> "
"to unselect any word as mentioned in the previous paragraph."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:676
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Working with the &kappname; editor"
msgid "Working with multiple cursors"
msgstr "&kappname; redaktori kasutamine"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:677
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you have created a few cursors, you can perform most of the editing "
"operations on them as you would on a single cursor. For example, typing a "
"letter will type it for each cursor. Similarly you can perform text "
"transforms &eg;, capitalization for all the positions or selections."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:681
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sometimes you will want to remove cursors. To do so, you can &Alt; + &LMB; "
"on the cursor that you want to remove. If you just want to remove cursors on "
"lines that are empty, there is a ready-made action for it that will do it "
"for you. To invoke the action, open the Command Bar using <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo> and look for "
"<guimenuitem>Remove cursors from empty lines</guimenuitem> and hit &Enter;. "
"You can also configure a shortcut for this action."
msgstr ""

